&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Product Designer at WorkBoard, you will shape experiences used across entire enterprises. You will work on complex design challenges that simplify how teams set goals, track progress, and accelerate results. You will also help bring thoughtful AI-powered and AI-First capabilities into real product workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fast-moving environment where priorities evolve quickly. You will do well here if you enjoy moving quickly, iterating often, and solving problems with just enough structure to make fast progress. You will collaborate closely with product managers, engineers, and other designers to explore ideas, refine solutions, and deliver intuitive, polished user experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What You’ll Do&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design end-to-end product experiences from concept to final UI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorporate AI and AI tools naturally into workflows where they improve clarity and speed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate research, customer insights, and strategy into clear interaction patterns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity designs to support fast decision cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with product managers and engineers in rapid, iterative development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to and extend our design system to ensure consistency and scalability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use qualitative and quantitative insights to validate design decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate design rationale clearly to keep teams aligned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
